50|$|<b>Fludroxycortide</b> (INN, BAN, JAN), {{also known}} as flurandrenolide (USAN) and flurandrenolone, is a {{synthetic}} topical corticosteroid and is used as an anti-inflammatory treatment for use on skin irritations. Trade names include Haelan (Typharm, UK) and Cordran (by Watson Pharmaceuticals, US).|$|E

